// SPECIALS_GUIDE - activity To create the game a litte more interesting, reflectors can appear randomly. Reflectors redirect the shoot and will be there for quite some time. If a bullet was redirected four times, reflectors won\'t influence the bullet direction anymore - it goes through the reflector.
